            <li><strong>Server port:</strong> 9001</li>
            <li><strong>Proxy:</strong> All requests to <code>/api</code> are proxied to <code>http://backend:9002</code> (Docker internal hostname). This means during development, the frontend dev server transparently forwards API calls to the backend without CORS issues.</li>
            <li><strong>Plugins:</strong> <code>@vitejs/plugin-react</code> for React Fast Refresh and JSX transform</li>
