            <li><code>target: ES2020</code> — Compiles to modern JavaScript</li>
            <li><code>module: ESNext</code> — Preserves ES module syntax for Vite to handle</li>
            <li><code>strict: true</code> — Enables all strict type-checking options</li>
            <li><code>jsx: react-jsx</code> — Uses the automatic JSX runtime (no need to import React in every file)</li>
            <li><code>moduleResolution: bundler</code> — Modern resolution algorithm compatible with Vite</li>
